g.text: ACORN BREWERY BRAND IDENTITY AND PACKAGING DESIGN
Acorn Brewery is run by A Couple Of Rednecks with an affinity for creating complex
yet tasty beers. They know their stuff but needed some branding and packaging made
for them to give them that creative edge to compete in the microbrewing craze
growing in the Northwest. I decided to push industrial efficiency and pepper some
retro colors and hand-craft flair on top for flavor.
